<script>
import Vue from 'vue';

import { Line, mixins } from 'vue-chartjs'
const { reactiveProp } = mixins

export default Vue.extend({
  mixins: [Line, reactiveProp],
  props: ['chartData', 'options'],
  mounted () {
    this.renderChart(this.chartData, this.options) 
  }
});
</script>
